---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="PICO IV CBD Infusion Therapy | Releaf MD" 
  description="Experience peak bioavailability with PICO IV CBD Infusions. Support your body's endocannabinoid system (ECS) under safe medical supervision."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(#1D8C64_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px] opacity-10"></div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-6 relative z-10">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3.5 py-1 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        💧 Latest Innovation in IV Hydration
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark leading-tight uppercase font-black">
        Now Offering PICO<br class="hidden sm:inline" /> IV CBD Infusions
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Gives your body peak access to the many potential benefits of cannabinoids. Administered through an IV so your body is able to absorb nearly 100% of the dose.
      </p>

      <!-- Key Benefits Row -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-8">
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-brand-primary/15 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-whisper text-left hover-lift flex gap-4">
          <div class="text-3xl">🛡️</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-base uppercase">Pure, Sterile, Safe</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1 leading-relaxed">
              This advanced CBD therapy offers significantly increased absorption compared to traditional oral supplements.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-brand-primary/15 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-whisper text-left hover-lift flex gap-4">
          <div class="text-3xl">🚀</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-base uppercase">Cutting Edge</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1 leading-relaxed">
              The latest medical innovation in IV hydration, designed specifically to help support your body's homeostasis.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 1: ECS & Natural Balance -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        
        <!-- Left Side: Core Concept (7 cols) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">
            Reboot Your Body’s Natural Balance System
          </h2>
          <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-brand-accent rounded-full"></div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            <p>
              Your body has a remarkable built-in network that helps keep everything running smoothly—from energy and sleep to stress response and immune function. It’s called the <strong>Endocannabinoid System (ECS)</strong>, and it’s working quietly behind the scenes to maintain internal balance.
            </p>
            <p>
              PICO IV is designed to support the ECS by delivering naturally occurring cannabinoids through IV infusion—offering a direct, efficient way to nourish one of your body’s most important regulatory systems.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-6">
            <div class="bg-brand-mint/30 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 space-y-3">
              <h4 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">
                The Endocannabinoid System: Your Body’s Balance Engine
              </h4>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                The ECS is a cellular communication network found throughout the body. It helps regulate key functions like mood, appetite, memory, inflammation, and recovery. Think of it like your body’s internal thermostat. When something pushes you out of balance—stress, fatigue, environmental toxins—the ECS helps restore equilibrium. But just like any system, it can fall behind when demand is high.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Side: CB1/CB2 Callout Box (5 cols) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark text-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-leaf border border-brand-primary/20 space-y-6 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -right-16 -top-16 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-primary/25 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <span class="text-3xl mb-4 block">🧬</span>
              <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-mint text-xl uppercase tracking-wider">
                CB1 & CB2: Tiny Gatekeepers with Big Jobs
              </h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
                The ECS operates through a network of receptors—tiny proteins on cell surfaces that respond to signals from within the body.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4 relative z-10 border-t border-brand-primary/25 pt-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-white">CB1 Receptors</h4>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-300 mt-1 leading-relaxed">
                  Found primarily in the brain and central nervous system. They help regulate mood, memory, stress response, appetite, and motor coordination.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-white">CB2 Receptors</h4>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-300 mt-1 leading-relaxed">
                  Mostly found in immune cells, the gut, and peripheral tissues. They help modulate immune activity and support the body’s natural response to external stressors.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-[11px] text-brand-accent italic font-semibold relative z-10 pt-2">
              Together, these receptors help your body adapt to change and maintain a state of internal balance.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Cannabinoids & Direct Support -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-brand-mint/30 border-t border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
        
        <!-- Left Column: Details -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">
            Cannabinoids & Direct Support
          </h2>
          <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-brand-accent rounded-full"></div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            <p>
              Your body makes its own cannabinoids (called endocannabinoids) to keep the ECS running. But some plants—like hemp—also produce similar compounds called phytocannabinoids. When introduced to the body, they can interact with ECS receptors.
            </p>
            <p>
              CBD is one of the best-known phytocannabinoids. It’s non-intoxicating, and when delivered intravenously, it bypasses digestion for fast, high-bioavailability absorption. In this way, it may help support ECS tone and signaling—especially when your body is under stress.
            </p>
            <p>
              Topical creams and oral supplements may offer limited absorption. <strong>PICO IV</strong> delivers broad spectrum cannabinoids directly into the bloodstream—offering rapid access to the ECS and minimizing loss through digestion or metabolism.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: Verification Spec Grid -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
          <div class="bg-white border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-whisper space-y-6">
            <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg uppercase tracking-wider text-center">
              Each Infusion is:
            </h3>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-4 rounded-xl text-center border border-brand-primary/10 hover-lift">
                <span class="text-2xl mb-1 block">🌿</span>
                <p class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-xs uppercase">THC-Free</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 mt-1">Non-psychoactive relief</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-4 rounded-xl text-center border border-brand-primary/10 hover-lift">
                <span class="text-2xl mb-1 block">🩺</span>
                <p class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-xs uppercase">Sterile & Tested</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 mt-1">Medical-grade purity</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-4 rounded-xl text-center border border-brand-primary/10 hover-lift">
                <span class="text-2xl mb-1 block">🇺🇸</span>
                <p class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-xs uppercase">USA Grown Hemp</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 mt-1">100% domestic hemp source</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-4 rounded-xl text-center border border-brand-primary/10 hover-lift">
                <span class="text-2xl mb-1 block">👩‍⚕️</span>
                <p class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-xs uppercase">Licensed Staff</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 mt-1">Carefully administered</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: When to Consider / Process / Science -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-16">
      
      <!-- Top Grid: ECS Support Criteria & Broad-Spectrum Science -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">When to Consider ECS Support</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Your ECS is always working, but when stress, overexertion, or illness overwhelm it, additional support may be beneficial. PICO IV is a personalized infusion designed to complement your body’s existing regulatory systems. It’s commonly used by those looking to promote overall balance and restore a sense of internal reset.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark text-white p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-brand-accent shadow-whisper space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-serif-headline text-brand-mint uppercase">Broad-Spectrum CBD, Backed by Science</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            PICO IV combines six powerful cannabinoids—<strong>CBD, CBG, CBN, CBD-A, CBG-A, and CBC</strong>—into a sterile, THC-free formulation. Every batch is rigorously third-party tested for purity, potency, and safety:
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 pt-2 text-[10px] text-brand-accent font-semibold uppercase">
            <div>✓ Grown from USA hemp</div>
            <div>✓ No pesticides or metals</div>
            <div>✓ Non-psychoactive</div>
            <div>✓ Legal in all 50 states</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom Timeline: How it Works -->
      <div class="space-y-8 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase text-center">How It Works</h3>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 relative">
          <!-- Connector line -->
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-6 left-6 right-6 h-0.5 bg-brand-primary/10 z-0"></div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-150 hover-lift text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">1</div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">Consultation</h4>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Meet with our staff to review your personal wellness goals.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-150 hover-lift text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">2</div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">Approval</h4>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed">A licensed provider approves your custom starting dose.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-150 hover-lift text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">3</div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">Administration</h4>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Your sterile infusion is administered safely in a clinical setting.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-150 hover-lift text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">4</div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">Follow-up</h4>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed">We conduct ongoing evaluations to ensure proper dosing over time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Interactive Accordion FAQ Section (White/Mint Canvas) -->
  <section id="faq" class="py-20 bg-brand-mint/50 border-t border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">Get answers to the most common queries regarding PICO IV CBD Infusions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-brand-primary/10 shadow-whisper overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover-lift">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none" data-faq="faq1" id="btn-faq1">
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">How long do the effects last?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-brand-primary font-bold text-sm transition-transform duration-300">＋</span>
          </button>
          <div id="faq1" class="faq-answer faq-answer-container">
            <div class="faq-answer-content px-6 pb-5 text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-50 pt-3">
              It varies—some feel benefit for several days, others for weeks. Everyone’s system is different.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-brand-primary/10 shadow-whisper overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover-lift">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none" data-faq="faq2" id="btn-faq2">
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">Are there side effects?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-brand-primary font-bold text-sm transition-transform duration-300">＋</span>
          </button>
          <div id="faq2" class="faq-answer faq-answer-container">
            <div class="faq-answer-content px-6 pb-5 text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-50 pt-3">
              Some people report temporary fatigue, dizziness, or upset stomach—especially at higher doses.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-brand-primary/10 shadow-whisper overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover-lift">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none" data-faq="faq3" id="btn-faq3">
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">Is this FDA approved?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-brand-primary font-bold text-sm transition-transform duration-300">＋</span>
          </button>
          <div id="faq3" class="faq-answer faq-answer-container">
            <div class="faq-answer-content px-6 pb-5 text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-50 pt-3">
              The FDA has not evaluated CBD for any specific conditions. PICO IV is not intended to diagnose, treat, or cure any disease.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-brand-primary/10 shadow-whisper overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover-lift">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none" data-faq="faq4" id="btn-faq4">
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">Who should not get PICO IV?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-brand-primary font-bold text-sm transition-transform duration-300">＋</span>
          </button>
          <div id="faq4" class="faq-answer faq-answer-container">
            <div class="faq-answer-content px-6 pb-5 text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-50 pt-3 space-y-2">
              <p>You should not receive PICO IV if you fall under any of the following:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-4 space-y-1">
                <li>Anyone with a prior history of allergy to CBD</li>
                <li>Pregnant or breastfeeding women</li>
                <li>Persons with a tendency to be hypotensive (chronic low blood pressure) may be at increased risk of lightheadedness.</li>
                <li>Persons with active bacterial infections may experience more post-treatment side effects due to the antibacterial effects of CBD, but can still receive treatment.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-brand-primary/10 shadow-whisper overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover-lift">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none" data-faq="faq5" id="btn-faq5">
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">Is it safe?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-brand-primary font-bold text-sm transition-transform duration-300">＋</span>
          </button>
          <div id="faq5" class="faq-answer faq-answer-container">
            <div class="faq-answer-content px-6 pb-5 text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-50 pt-3">
              Yes, PICO IV is safe. Our CBD is third-party tested and administered in sterile conditions by licensed professionals.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-brand-primary/10 shadow-whisper overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover-lift">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none" data-faq="faq6" id="btn-faq6">
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">Are there Clinical Studies Supporting the use of CBD?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-brand-primary font-bold text-sm transition-transform duration-300">＋</span>
          </button>
          <div id="faq6" class="faq-answer faq-answer-container">
            <div class="faq-answer-content px-6 pb-5 text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-50 pt-3 text-justify">
              Yes, there are hundreds of studies that have looked at the safety and benefits of CBD for a broad range of symptoms and medical conditions. However, the FDA has not evaluated the effects of CBD for any specific conditions. PICO IV CBD is not promoted to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-slate-200 mt-12 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
        <div class="space-y-1 text-center md:text-left">
          <p class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-dark">PICO CBD & NAD+ Infusion: <span class="text-brand-primary text-xl font-black">$209</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">Add any other IV therapy for only <span class="text-brand-accent font-bold">$150</span></p>
        </div>
        <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing/online-scheduling?service=1jsgl9ss2gy48bmm" class="bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-primary text-white font-bold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-xs uppercase transition-colors shadow-md active-press" id="btn-book-now">
          Book Appointment
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script data-astro-rerun>
    // FAQ Accordion Toggle with Smooth Transitions
    const toggles = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle');
    toggles.forEach(toggle => {
      toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const id = toggle.getAttribute('data-faq');
        const answer = document.getElementById(id);
        const icon = toggle.querySelector('.faq-icon');
        const isOpen = answer.classList.contains('is-open');

        // Close all answers
        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-answer').forEach(a => a.classList.remove('is-open'));
        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-icon').forEach(i => i.textContent = '＋');

        if (!isOpen) {
          answer.classList.add('is-open');
          icon.textContent = '－';
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
